column4: A 50-story high-rise apartment building in Tokyo. The apartment is 10 years old and has very good access to Tokyo Station. The redevelopment of the surrounding area is underway, and we can expect land prices to rise in the future.

A skyscraper currently under construction in Singapore. It is an extremely popular building whose tenants are already filled with a number of foreign companies, and the recruitment is expected to be completed by the end of this summer.
This hotel is located in Hakone, one of Japan's most famous hot spring areas. Hakone is very popular with tourists from all over the world every year. This property has been decided to be rebuilt.
A famous Resort in Hawaii. Although it is over 30 years old, it is very popular and always difficult to book.

The most popular resort in the Maldives. The building sits on top of the ocean, so you can enjoy 360-degree ocean views. Because of this, it is very popular with the wealthy, although the price of accommodation is expensive.
60-story tower blocks in Hong Kong. The lower floor is a shopping mall and the upper floor is used as offices for many famous companies.
